- **Core APIs**: `/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/packages/toolkit/src/schema/schema.ts`
- **Type Inference**: `/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/packages/toolkit/src/schema/infer-type.ts`
- **Helpers**: `/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/packages/toolkit/src/schema/helpers.ts`
- **TypeBox Wrapper**: `/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/packages/toolkit/src/schema/lib/type.ts`
- **Tests**: `/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/packages/toolkit/src/schema/__tests__/`

